3. Password Manager Setup

Ja, dmenu_pass kräver pass:
a) Installera Password Store
bash
Copy

sudo pacman -S pass  # Arch
sudo apt install pass # Debian

b) Initiera lösenordsbutik
bash
Copy

pass init "Your GPG Key"  # Ersätt med din GPG-nyckel
pass git init  # Valfritt: Versionshantering

c) Förbättrad dmenu_pass

Skapa ~/.local/bin/dmenu_pass:

#!/bin/sh
selected=$(find ~/.password-store/ -type f -name "*.gpg" | \
    sed 's|.*/.password-store/||; s/\.gpg$//' | \
    dmenu -i -l 15 -p " Pass:" -w 500)

[ -n "$selected" ] && pass show -c "$selected" && \
    notify-send -t 2000 "Password Copied" "$selected"

Gör den körbar:
chmod +x ~/.local/bin/dmenu_pass

Bind till tangent:
hc keybind Mod1+p spawn ~/.local/bin/dmenu_pass

4. dmenu_websearch - Förenklad Version

Skapa ~/.local/bin/dmenu_websearch:

#!/bin/sh
engine="https://duckduckgo.com/?q="
query=$(echo "" | dmenu -p "🔍 Search:" -w 600)
[ -n "$query" ] && xdg-open "${engine}${query}"

5. Extra Tips: Clipboard History

För en bättre clipboard-historik:

yay -S cliphist  # Arch

Lägg till i autostart:

wl-paste --watch cliphist store &  # Wayland
# ELLER
xclip -selection clipboard -o -watch | cliphist store &  # X11

